Winning numbers drawn in ‘Georgia FIVE Evening’ game
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Georgia FIVE Evening” game were:
6-0-5-2-4
(six, zero, five, two, four)
